summary: This document is a series of emails from February 2020 between an FBI Special Agent in New York and a 'LE Request' contact, likely at a travel or booking company, regarding a subpoena for information on Ghislaine Maxwell. The FBI is seeking additional identifying information (email addresses, credit card numbers, itinerary numbers) to locate booking records related to Maxwell.

persons.context: An FBI Special Agent from the New York Child Exploitation & Human Trafficking task force who sent a subpoena and is following up to obtain booking records related to Ghislaine Maxwell.

SAM is corresponding with Michelle, a contact at 'LE Request', to obtain information responsive to a subpoena regarding Ghislaine Maxwell.
Michelle's company ('LE Request') appears to hold booking records that may involve Ghislaine Maxwell, and is being asked to provide them via subpoena.

events.title: Subpoena received for Maxwell records
events.description: The 'LE Request' entity received a subpoena from the FBI (Special Agent SAM) regarding Ghislaine Maxwell.

events.title: Request for more identifying information
events.description: Michelle from LE Request emails SAM stating they need more identifying information (email addresses, credit card numbers, itinerary numbers) to locate booking records for Ghislaine Maxwell, as their databases lack DOB information.

keyFacts: In February 2020, the FBI's New York Child Exploitation & Human Trafficking task force was actively investigating Ghislaine Maxwell, issuing a subpoena for her booking records.

A company or service referred to as 'LE Request' received the subpoena but required more identifying information (email addresses, credit card numbers, or itinerary numbers) to search their databases, as they lacked date-of-birth information.
The FBI provided email addresses for Maxwell, but an initial search by 'LE Request' did not locate any bookings, prompting a request for confirmation or additional email addresses.
The correspondence shows the practical challenges law enforcement faced in obtaining travel or booking records for Maxwell without specific digital identifiers.
